  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 ! \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0bb0\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Celebrating Black July Memorial Day in Khalimagut! The artist who revealed the massacre of Tamil people through the music!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 39th anniversary of the Black July riots against the Tamil people was observed.",
        "On July 23, 1983, ethnic riots against the Tamil people were unleashed in Sri Lanka.",
        "During this, thousands of Tamil people from Colombo and other areas were looted, destroyed and driven northwards as refugees.",
        "In July 1983, JR. An event to remember the Tamil people who were massacred by thugs with the support of the Jayawardene government was held in Kalimugathidal area yesterday.",
        "Thus commemoration events were conducted in various places on the occasion of the 39th anniversary of Black July when the genocide against Tamils \u200b\u200bwas unleashed.",
        "In this case, artist Prabhutha Dhanushka had staged a river in Kalimugathidal to symbolize the brutal massacre of Tamil people in July 1983.",
        "It was staged in a heart-melting manner as a painful work of art by artist Prabhutha Dhanushka in memory of the massacred Tamil people.",
        "Meanwhile, a commemoration of the Tamil people who were massacred by government-backed Quails in July 1983 was held yesterday at the Boralai Cemetery in Colombo. It is noteworthy that the event was organized by the North-East-South-Malayalam-Diaspora Brotherhood."
      ],
